{
  "stem": "12462.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one time, in-- [CLEARS THROAT] in Germany, in Nuremberg, I must have had over 50 people working for me, making recommendations and assembling evidence to be put into volumes where the total record would not be published, because that was in mimeograph form, and it would be hundreds of thousands of pages.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to condense this and to put the main things in-- the indictment, and the opening statements, and the closing statements of both the prosecution and the defense, or at least a majority of the-- of the-- those statements, and then extracts from the evidence of both the prosecution, followed by the evidence of the defense.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what's published in those 15 green volumes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- we-- we started in-- it over in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- I should say we had over 50 people working on that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And over half of them were Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the defense counsel, Karl Hoffman, who had represented the defendant, Ambros, for example, in the IG Farben trial, very gladly came over and became a part of the publication staff.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we relied a great deal on him to be able to say, this is the best defense evidence, which was offered to respond to the prosecution evidence.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we put a selection in of the prosecution evidence, and we put a selection in of the defense evidence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people made their recommendations to me and a couple of my assistants.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, that's what became the official volumes on the last 12 trials.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I completed those-- the-- the editing of those volumes in late 1951, or maybe early in '51.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember, just now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd left Nuremberg in 1949.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
